statements: SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE report_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT report_id, patient_id FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE outcome_score > 80 ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE trend = 'Positive' LIMIT 10;
SELECT patient_id, outcome_score FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE report_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT AVG(outcome_score) AS avg_score FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE trend = 'Negative';
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE outcome_score > 80 ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT report_id, report_date FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE patient_id = 'abc123' ORDER BY report_date ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT patient_id, AVG(outcome_score) FROM telepsychiatry_reports GROUP BY patient_id;
SELECT report_date, SUM(outcome_score) FROM telepsychiatry_reports WHERE trend = 'Positive' GROUP BY report_date HAVING SUM(outcome_score) > 100;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_reports, MAX(outcome_score) AS max_score FROM telepsychiatry_reports;
SELECT * FROM telepsychiatry_outcomes;

SELECT trend_category, AVG(trend_value) AS avg_value FROM telepsychiatry_trends GROUP BY trend_category ORDER BY avg_value DESC

SELECT * FROM patients;
SELECT patient_name, patient_gender FROM patients;
SELECT DISTINCT patient_gender FROM patients;
SELECT patient_name, date_of_birth FROM patients WHERE patient_gender='Male';
SELECT treatment_type, start_date, end_date FROM treatments WHERE start_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE patient_gender = 'Male' ORDER BY patient_name DESC;

SELECT assessments.assessment_id, assessments.assessment_date, patients.patient_name FROM assessments JOIN patients ON assessments.patient_id = patients.patient_id WHERE assessments.score > 80 ORDER BY assessments.assessment_date ASC;

SELECT patients.patient_name, treatments.treatment_type, treatments.start_date, treatments.end_date FROM patients JOIN treatments ON patients.patient_id = treatments.patient_id WHERE treatments.end_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY patients.patient_name, treatments.start_date;

SELECT assessments.assessment_date, patients.patient_name, treatments.treatment_type FROM assessments JOIN patients ON assessments.patient_id = patients.patient_id JOIN treatments ON patients.patient_id = treatments.patient_id WHERE assessments.score < 50 ORDER BY assessments.assessment_date, patients.patient_name, treatments.treatment_type DESC;

SELECT assessments.score, treatments.treatment_type FROM assessments JOIN treatments ON assessments.patient_id = treatments.patient_id WHERE assessments.score BETWEEN 60 AND 80 ORDER BY assessments.score DESC;
SELECT * FROM reports;
SELECT report_id, patient_id, report_date FROM reports;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients;
SELECT * FROM psychiatrists WHERE specialization = 'Cognitive Behavioral Therapy';
SELECT trend_id, trend_date, trend_type FROM trends;
SELECT * FROM reports WHERE psychiatrist_id = 1;
SELECT report_id, report_date, outcome FROM reports WHERE patient_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY patient_name ASC;

SELECT psychiatrists.psychiatrist_name, reports.report_date, reports.outcome FROM psychiatrists JOIN reports ON psychiatrists.psychiatrist_id = reports.psychiatrist_id WHERE reports.outcome LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT trend_date, trend_type, trend_data->>'key' AS key_value FROM trends WHERE trend_type = 'health';
